/> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n證據呢證據呢"},{"pid":"089c4117fc2ad951179a19bd9f30ebb6d8c97fe5","tid":854163,"uid":34008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:41:07.000Z","msg":"「Lin Lin ..Lin Lin Lin」冇人開門既？<br />\n「啪啪啪..啪啪啪....」象仔大嗌:「開門呀，有冇人呀？我係象仔安東尼呀，嚟探湯瑪仕架~」<br />\n此時，木門緩緩地開啟，門後面露出一對金色發光既四方形大眼睛，象仔嚇到向後退！<br />\n<br />\n門後既人行咗出嚟，喺屋外既煤氣燈底下，我地可以見到...帶行山黑超既白熊先生。<br />\n白熊先生係湯瑪仕既爸爸，之前喺學校家長會安東尼已經見過佢嫁喇，當時大象媽媽仲有同對方打招呼添。"},{"pid":"23eb41d92836faf0e6eacf80904a4acb03c986ea","tid":854163,"uid":34008,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"比相大家幻想下先，依個係象仔安東尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SP99AoG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSP99AoG.png&h=719ef5e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1d2081d417c5382e9e7803a07f318ea5d2e935d","tid":854163,"uid":207414,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"23eb41d92836faf0e6eacf80904a4acb03c986ea","tid":854163,"uid":34008,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"比相大家幻想下先，依個係象仔安東尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SP99AoG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSP99AoG.png&h=719ef5e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/164651_fd9364418f0d493001ccf9a133f2a77b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F164651_fd9364418f0d493001ccf9a133f2a77b.png&h=a8e18b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安東尼你唔記得我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daae57ff69f0ae0937f0121e1200f55bcaf58dfd","tid":854163,"uid":34008,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"e1d2081d417c5382e9e7803a07f318ea5d2e935d","tid":854163,"uid":207414,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"23eb41d92836faf0e6eacf80904a4acb03c986ea","tid":854163,"uid":34008,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"比相大家幻想下先，依個係象仔安東尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SP99AoG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSP99AoG.png&h=719ef5e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/164651_fd9364418f0d493001ccf9a133f2a77b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F164651_fd9364418f0d493001ccf9a133f2a77b.png&h=a8e18b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安東尼你唔記得我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:13:42.000Z","msg":"你搞咩好似中輻射咁既樣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd781da1458590ce2c11fa2c30060b4800e4893","tid":854163,"uid":34008,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:15:39.000Z","msg":"安東尼從紅色格仔背囊入面拿出嗰罐$49.9既嘉x雜綿餅，用雙手好有誠意咁抱住，同白熊先生講：「白熊先生你好呀~我係湯瑪仕既同學呀，聽講佢病咗，我好擔心佢生性病呀，所以特登山長水遠嚟你地依啲山卡啦地方探下佢，佢冇事吖嘛？佢有事姐係我都會有事呀！」<br />\n白熊先生除低副黑超再摸摸下爬啲鬍鬚，同象仔講：「unmm多謝關心多謝關心。」<br />\n「依罐好野嚟嫁，醒你地既，居家旅行必備良藥呀。」<br />\n象仔將舖嘉x雜綿餅遞比白熊先生，對方接過之後講咗聲merci beaucoup，就大大力咁關咗門，得返象仔傻尻咁企咗喺門外。"},{"pid":"504fc8848c881b2e531947802c6dc60c1919e3bf","tid":854163,"uid":32691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:20:19.000Z","msg":"完"},{"pid":"a14711c12dcc98386a457f24da66b23ec7b1f1c7","tid":854163,"uid":207414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daae57ff69f0ae0937f0121e1200f55bcaf58dfd","tid":854163,"uid":34008,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"e1d2081d417c5382e9e7803a07f318ea5d2e935d","tid":854163,"uid":207414,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"23eb41d92836faf0e6eacf80904a4acb03c986ea","tid":854163,"uid":34008,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"比相大家幻想下先，依個係象仔安東尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SP99AoG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSP99AoG.png&h=719ef5e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/164651_fd9364418f0d493001ccf9a133f2a77b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F164651_fd9364418f0d493001ccf9a133f2a77b.png&h=a8e18b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安東尼你唔記得我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:13:42.000Z","msg":"你搞咩好似中輻射咁既樣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:25:30.000Z","msg":"病咗咪變到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28ef0fc0db16ab96611e557d4d5dcdc45087961","tid":854163,"uid":3527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:38:08.000Z","msg":"我到底睇咗啲乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ee7367fd01cc896dbb1dd9f98dc5e80c57f9ef","tid":854163,"uid":34008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:44:21.000Z","msg":"象仔安東尼此刻心諗「咩料呀，開返度門先啦，我嚟到講唔夠一分鐘就竟然被拒於門外，唔得！我係唔會咁易放棄嫁！」<br />\n「喂開門呀白熊先生！我未講完呀！」幽靜既森林裡面傳來一陣又一陣有節奏既啪啪啪啪啪聲，令人想入非非，但始終都係未有人開門。<br />\n<br />\n「仆街還錢呀！！！」依個時候象仔唯有使出殺手鐧。<br />\n唔洗半秒，門就即刻開返，白熊先生說：「又點呀？夜喇過主啦小朋友，唔好喺我屋企門口嘈生曬了，我報警嫁！」<br />\n「唔好呀...其實我淨係想見下湯瑪仕咋...你比我入屋先啦，出面好凍呀嗚.....」委屈咗半日既象仔終於流下眼淚，流呀流，流呀流，佢內心深處既悲傷都隨眼淚留出嚟，最後留返喺心既只有安東尼對湯瑪仕既愛。"},{"pid":"851b54be20138162a8648a6c3852e8f04f3a1ae3","tid":854163,"uid":34008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a14711c12dcc98386a457f24da66b23ec7b1f1c7","tid":854163,"uid":207414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"daae57ff69f0ae0937f0121e1200f55bcaf58dfd","tid":854163,"uid":34008,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"e1d2081d417c5382e9e7803a07f318ea5d2e935d","tid":854163,"uid":207414,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T08:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/09/164651_fd9364418f0d493001ccf9a133f2a77b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F09%2F164651_fd9364418f0d493001ccf9a133f2a77b.png&h=a8e18b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n安東尼你唔記得我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:13:42.000Z","msg":"你搞咩好似中輻射咁既樣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:25:30.000Z","msg":"病咗咪變到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:46:15.000Z","msg":"好擔心你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉食餅啦食餅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d9260fcad1258ad9a3ecf3744c3a23eeaab102","tid":854163,"uid":16584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a28ef0fc0db16ab96611e557d4d5dcdc